<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.3">
<l>vātaivan taṭara vāṉamum nilaṉum malaikaḷu malaikaṭal kuḷippa</l>
<l>mītukoṇ ṭukaḷum mīṉuru vāki viripuṉal variyakaṭ ṭoḷittōṉ</l>
<l>pōtalar puṉṉai mallikai mauval putuvirai matumala raṇaintu</l>
<l>cītavoṇ teṉṟal ticaitoṟuṅ kamaḻun tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When torment came and oppressed [the world], as the heavens, earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">and mountains were hidden in the roiling sea,</l>
<l>The one who, taking the form of a fish which frolicked, bearing [them] to the</l>
<l rend="indent">surface, concealed the spreading waters in [his] striped belly,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi where laurels with buds just opening,</l>
<l rend="indent">jasmine, wild jasmine,</l>
<l>[And] new, fragrant, honeyed blossoms, combining in the fine south wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">scent every quarter.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
